  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that a <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Regency_of_Aegon_III)\" title=\"High Septon (Regency of Aegon III)\">High Septon</a> forbade Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Hightower\" title=\"Lyonel Hightower\">Lyonel Hightower</a> from marrying his widowed step-mother, <a href=\"/index.php/Samantha_Tarly\" title=\"Samantha Tarly\">Samantha Tarly</a>, as it was considered a form of <a href=\"/index.php/Incest\" title=\"Incest\">incest</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/128&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aftermath - The Hour of the Wolf.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404032111\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 116/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 404/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument